Package camzup.core

Class Entity3

java.lang.Object
camzup.core.Entity
camzup.core.Entity3
All Implemented Interfaces:
IEntity, IUtils
Direct Known Subclasses:
CurveEntity3, MeshEntity3
public class Entity3
extends Entity
An entity in three dimensional space that can be moved around with a transform, but contains no other data. Useful when a 'target' entity is needed.
